		array('Okay don\'t panic! Alright? Stop panicking! I can still stop this. Ahh. Oh there\'s a password.  It\'s fine. I\'ll just hack it. Not a problem... umm...', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/c/c8/Wheatley_sp_a1_wakeup_hacking08.wav'),
