		array('Hey! How\'s it going! I talked my way onto the nanobot work crew rebuilding this shaft. They are REALLY small, so -ah - I KNOW, Jerry. No, I\'m on BREAK, mate. On a break.', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/f/f9/Wheatley_nanobotinto09.wav'),
