		array('[to JERRY] See you in court, mate. [to player] Anyway, look, just hang in there for five more chambers.', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/1/1a/Wheatley_nanobotow03.wav'),
		array('Hey, buddy!', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/6/6a/Wheatley_jailbreakdooropens01.wav'),
