		array('Oh for God\'s... They told me if I ever turned this flashlight on, I would DIE. They told me that about EVERYTHING.  I don\'t know why they even bothered to give me this stuff if they didn\'t want me to use it. It\'s pointless. Mad.', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/d/d6/Wheatley_sphere_flashlight_tour72.wav'),
