		array('Oh! But I did find something. Reminds me: I\'ve got a big surprise for you two. Seriously. Look forward to it.', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/8/8a/Wheatley_bw_sp_a4_speed_tb_catch_solve02.wav'),
