		array('I KNOW, Jerry. No, I\'m on BREAK, mate. On a break.', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/f/fd/Wheatley_nanobotonbreak01.wav'),
		array('Anyway, we\'re really close to busting out. Just hang in there for - OW!', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/2/26/Wheatley_nanobotinto08.wav'),
