		array('Here\'s an interesting story. I almost got a job down here in Manufacturing. Guess who the foreman went with? Only an exact duplicate of himself. Nepotism. Ended up giving me the WORST possible job: tending to all the smelly humans. The umm... Sorry about that. That just slipped out.', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/7/7f/Wheatley_sphere_flashlight_tour71.wav'),
