		array('I was going to kill you fast. With bullets. Or neurotoxin. But if you\'re going to pull stunts like this, it doesn\'t have to be fast. So you know. I\'ll take my time.', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/2/27/GLaDOS_fgbwheatleyentrance10.wav'),
