		array('You can\'t keep going like this forever, you know. I\'m GOING to find out what you\'re doing. Out there. Where I can\'t see you. I\'ll know. All I need is proof.', 'http://i1.theportalwiki.net/img/a/ae/GLaDOS_sp_paint_jump_redirect_bomb_entry01.wav'),
